snippet.title: Give My Regards To Broad Street - Playthrough (C64)
snippet.description:
Regards aplenty as a potentially drunken Paul McCartney gallivants and crashes his way around London in his custom Ford Popular, on a quest to meet up with his band mates at various tube stations to collect the missing notes to "No More Lonely Nights".

I found all the notes, returned to Abbey Road Studio and mixed the song but whether or not I won the game, I have no idea. Final Score: 4,763 (For whatever that's worth.)
